<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Admin Disabled - Chainhoist Database</title>
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    body {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a1a2e 0%, #16213e 100%);
      min-height: 100vh;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
    }
    .card {
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.95);
      border-radius: 16px;
      padding: 2.5rem;
      box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
      max-width: 500px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .icon { font-size: 4rem; color: #dc3545; }
    code {
      background: #f8f9fa;
      padding: 0.2rem 0.5rem;
      border-radius: 4px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="card">
    <div class="icon">&#128274;</div>
    <h2 class="mt-3">Admin Panel Disabled</h2>
    <p class="text-muted">The admin panel is not configured.</p>
    <hr>
    <p class="small text-start">To enable, set the <code>ADMIN_PASSWORD</code> environment variable:</p>
    <pre class="text-start bg-light p-3 rounded small">ADMIN_PASSWORD=your-secure-password</pre>
    <a href="/" class="btn btn-outline-dark mt-3">Back to Database</a>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
